Class GenerationManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • logic.GenerationManager
  • Deprecated. 
    Reason: class is not fully operable and will not be ready in time for the deadline. For later versions the Generation-manager could be used to gather statistics be utilising the generation-pool.

    @Deprecated
public class GenerationManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class manages Generation-objects. It stores the generations in a Generation-pool. This way the user can navigate to previous generations. The generation-pool has a default cap of 50 generations, but can be expanded.
